result.name: The Grand Buffet

reviews.text:
The revolving restuarant with gorgeous view of HK.  Food are excellent, great varieties.  
Very nice service, although I am surprised that one of the bus ladies said "靚女，仲要唔要?"  I thought I was at a local Chinese restuarant...🤨 .

A massive buffet! There is a huge choice of cuisines (Japanese, Indian, Chinese) to choose from so come hungry.
The thrill of the restaurant starts with getting there! The exterior bubble elevator is impressive giving you quite a ride up to the restaurant. Once in restaurant, the views of Hong Kong are beautiful.
But take note that you have to pay quite a bit for this experience.

The food was generally good quality and service very good for price.

However, there are two major issues that standout and prevent a better rating. One issue is food preparation & service and the other was quality.

Snow crab is only served chilled rather than steamed with drawn butter and lemon and was a let down. Not only is chilled crab not as flavorful, it makes the meat stick to the shell.

The roast beef was of poor quality; it was laced with grizzle and very tough.

Highlights here are the view and variety.

Good location and view. Visited for dinner buffet and recommend to go there before 630 so you can see the sunset and take more photo with view and less guests nearby... After turning dark, no view can be clearly seen via camera. I guess view would be more spectacular in bright day?

Good variety of food. You can find dim sum, oyster, beef, goose liver, fried ice cream, lobster, etc . Signature highlighted all can be found.

Birthday dessert with birthday plate can be preordered and costs $50+ . You can request window seat but not necessary as all seats are crowdedly pack along window anyway. You may feel dizzy if too close to window ...
Wide variety for selection with good quality food.  Good ambiance as well

result.name: 自助山

reviews.text:
非常愉快的经历，昨天在网上预约了今天中午12点-2:30的时间，到了以后发现我们的位子不靠窗，跟领班说可不可以给我们换到窗口，最后真的有空位给我们，太感谢了！
食物也很美味，新鲜，甜点也不腻且非常好看。
大人差不多300多一个人小孩十岁以下的270左右，平时的中午场，个人认为价格实惠。转一圈差不多两个小时，慢慢吃正好。下次如果再来香港还要来这里。工作人员服务都非常友好，谢谢🙏
好專業的服務，食品款式多，唔會有趕住走快D食快D埋單的感覺，非常好感覺好悠閒，缺點是餐廳地下轉得太快，有D頭昏昏感覺

บัฟเฟตต์ หมุน 360 องศา บนความสูง 62 ชั้น,อารหารหลากหลาย เหมาะกับราคา,พนักงานบริการดี มีความสุภาพมาก,อาหารรสชาดออกกลาง ๆ,อาหารประเภทขนมหวาน ขนมจีบรสชาดอร่อย,ได้บรรยากาศวิวตึกสูง ท่าเรือฮ่องกง ในช่วงกลางคืนกลายเป็นวิวแสงไฟ จากมุมสูง,ไม่ถือว่าแพง หรือถูก สมราคาน่าจะถูกต้องที่สุด
合和頂層自助餐，特別之處賣點，旋轉餐廳，即晚餐時，如坐在窗邊的話，整個維港景就在你眼前，好靚，整體食物做得唔錯，服務ok，食物種類亦多，價錢合理，因在進食時，有不同的風景係眼前，已值回票價，大家如想試試，需訂位及兩段進餐時間揀選，第一段，大約1800起，第二段，大約2000起，大家到時留意揀選

reviews.text:
The service is nice & the food is quick to be delivered at your table.
The prices are reasonably cheap given the combinations offered.
Although this Mall has been established for many years, trendy, head fi, watches, stuff can be found there
It's very convinient, that area has thr grocery shops, close to restaurants. And very accessible to transportation.

A good example of best architecture. 17th floor connects to hill top exit. Where one can catch a taxi from without going to the Ground. Ground Floor exit has McClaren and Tesla Car Showrooms near by. And, all the eateries. Feasible to find lunch in no time. Clean place having Mc Donalds to grab a quick breakfast meal or that strong coffee from Starbucks if you missed it.
Go for the all you can eat restaurant,  it circulates and you get great views of Hong Kong.

reviews.text: 好👌
當天我是有心進入 合和中心 地庫的 Taste 超級市場買東西，原來它是屬於 百佳 的，內裡地方好Q大，甚麼貨品都有。我就是在全灣仔區至銅鑼灣區都找不到的 Johnson BB爽身粉，好彩此店有五樽，我立即全部掃光。
一棟圓柱體的大廈，好特別，頂樓有出名的自座山 buffet, 可以一試
因為同喜歡嘅人喺優美嘅環境共進晚餐慶祝生日需要畀五分但係冇參考價值
